dct_title_s: Facsimile of the Ordnance Surveyors' drawings of the London area 1799-1808  / general editor, Ann Loreille Saunders ; with an introduction by Yolanda Hudson
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Includes a triangulation diagram: "For the improvement of the plan of London and its environments". Includes introductory notes. © London Topographical Society.
